BT Funds Management (International) Ltd.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 26, 2017 2:52 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of BT Funds Management (International) Ltd.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
BT Funds Management (International) Ltd. is an Iowa-based investment advisor with over $17.71 billion in assets under management. The firms equity strategy includes large-cap, growth, quantitative, and growth and value. It invests globally, specifically in the United States, France, Europe, Germany, Hong Kong, Japan, and Australia. BT Funds Management was established in 1969 and is based in Des Moines, Iowa. BT Funds Management (International) Ltd. operates as a subsidiary of Principal Financial Group Inc.


1900 Hub Tower699 WalnutDes Moines, IA 50309United StatesFounded in 1969



Phone: 515-247-6582

Fax: 515-248-2092

www.btfunds.com.au







